I think this is a direction that needs to be followed now, Kalovsk<0xC3><0xBD> said.
But the Ministry of Health does not want to change the pneumococcal vaccination process.
We are absolutely not considering it at the moment, said his spokesman Vlastimil Sr<0xC5><0xA1>e<0xC5><0x88>.
